personGenderSearchParameter

Parameter gender:token

Searches based on the gender of the person. Note that this value must be from the AdministrativeGender valueset eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Person?gender={gender}

ResourcePerson
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesPerson
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
